<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437986>
    dc:description "FIGURE 52. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. A. Oiovelia brasiliensis. B. Oiovelia cunucunumana. C. Oiovelia machadoi. D. Oiovelia viannai. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438288>
    dc:description "FIGURE 51. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Veliidae. A. Oiovelia brasiliensis, apterous male from Teresópolis, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4511, −43.0012). B. Oiovelia cunucunumana, macropterous male from Divinópolis, Minas Gerais (−20.2594, −44.9158).C. Oiovelia machadoi, macropterous male from Teresópolis, Rio de Janeiro (−22.446, −42.890).D. Oiovelia viannai, apterous male from Divinópolis, Minas Gerais (−20.2594, −44.9158). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438288/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

